Package lt.viko.eif.mjakovcenko.bankapp.model

Class Client

java.lang.Object
lt.viko.eif.mjakovcenko.bankapp.model.Client
@Entity public class Client extends Object
Client class represents client data. It loads data about this class from database. It has one-to-one connection with account and one-to-many connection with bank account.
